author: The Current
description:
Slug of @atmospheresucks talked with Nil from The Current’s Morning Show about what fans can expect at an Atmosphere show.

Atmosphere will be performing this Saturday, August 23 as part of The Current’s Music On-A-Stick featuring Cypress Hill, Lupe Fiasco, The Pharcyde and DJ Abilities.

title: Slug talks about what fans can expect at an Atmosphere show

author: The Current
description:
Music-inspired Crop Art at the 2025 Minnesota State Fair
Support The Current: https://support.mpr.org/youtube or hit the Thanks button

There are always mutual influences between music and the visual arts, and that interplay is evident in the Crop Art display at the Minnesota State Fair. The 2025 yield of Crop Art on exhibit in the Horticulture Building includes work that honors Prince, Bob Dylan, Aretha Franklin, Björk, Radiohead, Beyoncé and many others, plus a cheeky reference to Hall & Oates … and even a nod to The Current’s 20th anniversary! Watch the video above to see those The Current was able to capture during a visit to the State Fair’s ever-popular Crop Art display.
